OL,3,CMen guilty of murdering man found
OL,4,C'chopped up' in suitcases
OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder after a dad was discovered
OL,8,F'chopped up' in suitcases in a
OL,9,FManchester park in January.
OL,11,FThe 34-year-old victim, Ashley Walsh,
OL,12,Fhad gone for a drink with his friends
OL,13,FAaron Evitt and Gerard McGlacken.
OL,15,FThen, following a row at McGlacken's
OL,16,Fflat in Collyhurst, Evitt hit Mr Walsh
OL,17,Fover the head with a hammer, on 7
OL,18,FJanuary.
