OL,3,CMen guilty of murdering man found
OL,4,C'chopped up' in suitcases
OL,6,FHe led officers to Sand Hills park in
OL,7,FCollyhurst, a five minute walk away
OL,8,Ffrom McGlacken's flat, the scene of
OL,9,Fthe murder.
OL,11,FA pathologist examined Mr Walsh's
OL,12,Fremains following the discovery.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found that
OL,15,FMr Walsh had been 'dismembered through
OL,16,Fthe neck, central torso, both upper
OL,17,Farms close to the shoulders, both
OL,18,Fupper thighs, and his left lower leg'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
