OL,6,FSuspicions were raised about Evitt and
OL,7,FMcGlacken after they were seen on CCTV
OL,8,Fwith Mr Walsh's dog Duke, as the pair
OL,9,Fwere said to be 'inseparable'.
OL,11,FThe two men, who were uncle and
OL,12,Fnewphew, were arrested and both
OL,13,Fcharged with murder and both pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to preventing a lawful burial
OL,15,Fbut denied murder.
OL,17,FEvitt told jurors that a fight had
OL,18,Fbroken out in McGlacken's flat after
OL,19,FMr Walsh told Evitt that he'd slept
OL,20,Fwith his ex-girlfriend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
