OL,3,CMen guilty of murdering man found
OL,4,C'chopped up' in suitcases
OL,6,FAaron Evitt and his uncle Gerard
OL,7,FMcGlacken, now both face life
OL,8,Fsentences.
OL,10,FEvitt, of Brentnor Road, Moston, and
OL,11,FMcGlacken, of Kintore Walk, Collyhurst
OL,12,Fwere both unanimously convicted of
OL,13,Fmurder. They will be sentenced
OL,14,Ftomorrow.
OL,16,FMembers of Mr Walsh's family wore
OL,17,Fpurple jumpers in his memory as the
OL,18,Fverdicts were delivered.
